  <brief_title>Retrospective/Prospective Data Collection on the LDR ROIC Interbody Fusion Device With VerteBRIDGE Plating</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Clinical Study of the Safety and Efficacy of the ROI-C Anterior Cervical Interbody Fusion Device Using the VerteBRIDGE Plating System</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>LDR Spine USA</agency>
